  "id": "ASB-A-151095871",
  "summary": "[Lock Screen Bypass / Hidden Contents Shown on Lock Screen / Add new users to Pixel device from Lock Screen Transition ]",
  "details": "In several functions of KeyguardServiceWrapper.java and related files,, there is a possible way to briefly view what's under the lockscreen due to a race condition. This could lead to local escalation of privilege if a Guest user is enabled, with no additional execution privileges needed. User interaction is not needed for exploitation.",
